{
  "stem": "24268.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to send right away, ship them out for-- for [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Never Land. ?] And I, that time, I had a very nice Jewish doctor, with the Jewish-- [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Rena ?], her name was, which was in like in Red Cross, sort of, helping all the sick people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And obviously they kept quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the lagerfuhrer knew that I was-- he allowed me six weeks to be in bed, even.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my daddy came, and they came every day, and they took [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was not-- whatever medication was available, they tried to alleviate the pain.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They took all of the pus every day, and try to help me to heal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It didn't heal so well, but finally I got some relief.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the judenalteste, if they couldn't go to kitchen anymore, he told me want to stay on the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That means in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was some other things, so until it heals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So after that, I was surprised that they kept me that long, because of-- most the people, they don't, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't the sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't put me in the sick room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in the-- in the room with all the girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came to my room and did this all, which was very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise, I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They love me because I used to sing well, and I think the voice was so good, and I-- I don't know what the reason Daddy come.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think everything, people knew us, something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A lot of people didn't know, and for some reason, I-- I remain in the room, and somehow they did not send me away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shortly after that, there was a [? rumor-- ?] that if I'm correct, my daddy-- they took away clothes from us, too.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
